text: Hello! How are you?
I'm doing well, thanks! How about you?
I'm good too. What's up?
Just working on a project. How about you?
Same here! It's been quite hectic.
I can imagine. Any weekend plans?
Not really, just planning to relax. You?
Might catch up on some reading. Any book recommendations?
Yes, you should check out 'Atomic Habits' by James Clear.
Oh, I've heard good things about that one! Adding it to my list.
Do let me know how you like it!
Definitely will. Have you read anything else recently?
Yeah, I finished 'The Alchemist' a few days ago. It's a classic.
Oh wow, that's on my list too! Seems like I have a lot of reading to do.
Haha, take your time! It’s worth it though.
For sure! I'll start with 'Atomic Habits'.
Great choice!
Talk to you later?
Sure, have a great day!
Thanks, you too!
Hey, are you free to chat?
Yeah, just a moment. What's up?
I needed some help with a coding issue I'm stuck on.
Sure! Let me know the details, and I'll see what I can do.
I'm trying to implement a chat app. The messages aren't displaying properly.
Ah, I’ve worked on something similar. Have you checked the component structure?
Not really. Can you guide me through?
Sure! First, check how you're passing props to the message component.
Got it! Let me try that and get back to you.
No problem! Take your time.
